data.description: Come see your new house! You'll want to see everything this property has to offer in The Glen at Widefield. With 2,100 square feet, 4 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms, there is plenty of room for everyone, including guests! The open area of the living room greets you on the main level, followed by the kitchen. Access the back yard from the kitchen as well, making the patio an ideal spot for barbecuing. A firepit is fun for additional activities and spending a cool evening under the stars. The main level primary bedroom is adjoining to the main level bathroom, don't forget the walk-in closet. Use the main level's second bedroom for kids, crafts or even an office if you can work from home. You'll find a large family room with an additional two bedrooms and bathroom in the basement. This can offer guests privacy if they're staying for a few days. The utility room doubles as storage space for seasonal decorations or some of those extra things we inevitably collect. Don't miss out, book a showing today!
